flowchart TD
    %% Client Request
    Client["Streamlit UI<br/>(User asks: 'How are Apple's margins?')"]

    %% Gateway Layer
    Gateway{"API Gateway<br/>(Rate Limiter to protect LLM costs)"}

    %% RAG Engine (FastAPI)
    subgraph FastAPI RAG Engine
        Embed_Query["1. Embed Query<br/>(Convert text to vector)"]
        Search_DB["2. Vector Similarity Search<br/>(Find top-k chunks)"]
        Fetch_Live["3. Fetch Live Metrics<br/>(Internal REST Call)"]
        Build_Context["4. Construct Context Prompt<br/>(Combine text + metrics)"]
    end

    %% External Systems
    DB_Vector[("pgvector<br/>(Returns relevant<br/>transcript chunks)")]
    API_Spring["Spring Boot API<br/>(Returns live margins)"]
    LLM(("LLM Provider<br/>(OpenAI/Claude)"))

    %% The Flow
    Client -->|POST /api/v1/chat| Gateway
    Gateway -->|Forward Request| Embed_Query
    
    Embed_Query --> Search_DB
    
    Search_DB -->|Cosine Similarity| DB_Vector
    DB_Vector -->|Top 5 Excerpts| Build_Context
    
    Search_DB -.->|Identify Ticker| Fetch_Live
    Fetch_Live -->|GET /api/v1/metrics| API_Spring
    API_Spring -->|JSON Metrics| Build_Context

    Build_Context -->|Final Prompt Payload| LLM
    LLM -- "Streamed AI Response" --> Client